'cause no one helps me.

1063
01:05:38.796 --> 01:05:40.937
<i>(Breathing heavily)</i>

1064
01:05:47.046 --> 01:05:48.875
When I was a kid,

1065
01:05:48.979 --> 01:05:51.809
