in spirit.

1174
01:12:18.264 --> 01:12:20.957
Don't not believe that.

1175
01:12:21.060 --> 01:12:22.510
<i>(Sobs)</i>

1176
01:12:22.614 --> 01:12:25.133
And you've got Mr. Tibbs...

1177
01:12:25.237 --> 01:12:27.860
and Ava.

1178
01:12:32.486 --> 01:12:35.661
- <i>(Creaking)</i>
- Okay, time to go.

1179
01:12:38.008 --> 01:12:41.184
