you pull the cord.

1180
01:12:41.287 --> 01:12:43.117
All right?

1181
01:12:43.220 --> 01:12:45.568
Okay, let's do this.

1182
01:12:45.671 --> 01:12:49.123
<i>(Breathing heavily)</i>

1183
01:12:53.990 --> 01:12:55.163
