- I'm right behind you.

1196
01:14:30.604 --> 01:14:33.296
<i>(Both inhale deeply)</i>

1197
01:14:41.235 --> 01:14:44.341
<i>(Breathing heavily)</i>

1198
01:14:47.103 --> 01:14:49.001
<i>(Inhales deeply)</i>

1199
01:14:56.526 --> 01:14:59.702
<i>(Breathing heavily)</i>

